"plan-num\">PLAN 03</span>\n503\t      <span class=\"plan-name\">スタンダードプラン</span>\n504\t      <span class=\"plan-sub\">バランス型</span>\n505\t    </div>\n506\t    <div class=\"plan-btn\" data-plan=\"3\" role=\"radio\" aria-checked=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">\n507\t      <span class=\"plan-num\">PLAN 04</span>\n508\t      <span class=\"plan-name\">プレミアムプラン</span>\n509\t      <span class=\"plan-sub\">アップセル</span>\n510\t    </div>\n511\t  </div>\n512\t</section>\n513\t\n514\t<!-- ── Formula Bar ── -->\n515\t<div class=\"formula-bar\">\n516\t  <span>総額</span> = 基本出演料 × 使用期間 × 競合排除 × 業界 × メディア × 出演者ランク × マージン\n517\t</div>\n518\t\n519\t<!-- ── Main ── -->\n520\t<div class=\"container\">\n521\t\n522\t  <!-- Base Fee -->\n523\t  <section class=\"section\">\n524\t    <div class=\"section-label\">Base Fee</div>\n525\t    <div class=\"section-title\">基本出演料を入力</div>\n526\t    <div class=\"base-fee-card\">\n527\t      <label>ショートドラマ出演時のキャスティング費（税別）</label>\n528\t      <div class=\"input-row\">\n529\t        <span>¥</span>\n530\t        <input type=\"text\" class=\"base-fee-input\" id=\"baseFee\" placeholder=\"100,000\" value=\"100,000\" inputmode=\"numeric\" aria-label=\"基本出演料\">\n531\t      </div>\n532\t    </div>\n533\t  </section>\n534\t\n535\t  <!-- Coefficients -->\n536\t  <section class=\"section\">\n537\t    <div class=\"section-label\">Coefficients</div>\n538\t    <div class=\"section-title\">各係数を選択してください</div>\n539\t    <div class=\"coeff-grid\" id=\"coeffGrid\"></div>\n540\t  </section>\n541\t\n542\t  <!-- Reference -->\n543\t  <section class=\"section\">\n544\t    <div class=\"section-label\">Reference</div>\n545\t    <div class=\"section-title\">出演者ランク別 基本出演料の目安</div>\n546\t    <div class=\"ref-table-wrap\">\n547\t      <table class=\"ref-table\">\n548\t        <thead>\n549\t          <tr><th>ランク</th><th>係数</th><th>説明</th><th>基本出演料目安</th></tr>\n550\t        </thead>\n551\t        <tbody>\n552\t          <tr><td>新人A</td><td>×0.8</td><td>GOKKO専属新人</td><td>5万円</td></tr>\n553\t          <tr><td>新人B</td><td>×1.0</td><td>一般新人キャスト</td><td>8〜12万円</td></tr>\n554\t          <tr><td>準中堅</td><td>×1.8</td><td>実績ある若手</td><td>15〜25万円</td></tr>\n555\t          <tr><td>中堅A</td><td>×2.5</td><td>中堅タレント</td><td>30〜40万円</td></tr>\n556\t          <tr><td>中堅B</td><td>×3.5</td><td>人気中堅タレント</td><td>50〜80万円</td></tr>\n557\t          <tr><td>準有名</td><td>×5.0</td><td>知名度上昇中</td><td>80〜120万円</td></tr>\n558\t          <tr><td>有名A</td><td>×8.0</td><td>有名タレント</td><td>150〜300万円</td></tr>\n559\t          <tr><td>有名S</td><td>×12.0</td><td>トップクラス</td><td>500万円以上</td></tr>\n560\t        </tbody>\n561\t      </table>\n562\t    </div>\n563\t  </section>\n564\t</div>\n565\t\n566\t<!-- ── Sticky Result ── -->\n567\t<div class=\"result-panel\" id=\"resultPanel\">\n568\t  <div class=\"result-inner\">\n569\t    <div class=\"result-left\">\n570\t      <div class=\"result-plan-badge\" id=\"resultPlanBadge\">STANDARD</div>\n571\t      <div class=\"result-breakdown\" id=\"resultBreakdown\"></div>\n572\t    </div>\n573\t    <div class=\"result-total\">\n574\t      <div class=\"result-total-label\">Estimated Total</div>\n575\t      <div class=\"result-total-value\" id=\"resultValue\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\">¥0</div>\n576\t    </div>\n577\t  </div>\n578\t  <div class=\"sr-only\" id=\"resultLiveRegion\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\"></div>\n579\t</div>\n580\t\n581\t<!-- ── Footer ── -->\n582\t<footer class=\"footer\">\n583\t  © <span class=\"copyright-year\">2026</span> GOKKO Inc. All rights reserved. ｜ 本料金表は参考価格です。正式なお見積りは別途ご相談ください。\n584\t</footer>\n585\t\n586\t</div><!-- /app-content -->\n587\t\n588\t<script>\n589\t// ═══════════════════════════════════════\n590\t// PLAN DATA — 4 plans × 5 coefficient categories\n591\t// ═══════════════════════════════════════\n592\tconst PLANS = [\n593\t  // ── PLAN 0: ライトプラン（フック重視）──\n594\t  {\n595\t    name: 'ライトプラン',\n596\t    nameEn: 'LIGHT',\n597\t    period: [\n598\t      { label: '1ヶ月', coeff: 0.8, desc: 'お試し配信'